          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人头号令在营前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刀斧手押谭雄同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，贤侄，今日初次出兵，就擒来仇人谭雄，真虎将也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍，看宴伺候，今当与二位皇侄贺功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将军，你也来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在大营排宴把酒饮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫一声二贤侄细听分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "擒来了吴将显威名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "胜似蜀营众老臣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "适才间营外来对阵"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "理当分功把赏论"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言来怒气生，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我主说话太欺情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "分明笑我老无能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "适才间营外来对阵"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "理当分功把赏论"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，向那关兴、张苞，乃是子侄之辈，阵前擒来谭雄，无非是些许一点功劳；"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我主隆恩，在酒席宴前，夸了又夸，奖了又奖，分明是笑我老将无用。也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不免私自出营，去到阵前，匹马单刀，生擒潘璋，活捉吴侯。那时方显俺"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄忠不老！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "适才间营外来对阵"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "理当分功把赏论"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "胸中妙计安排稳，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "去至阵前会敌人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "要学当年取定军。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄忠下。报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄老将军，私自出营，叫阵去了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言来心内惊，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "营中气坏老将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "快快保护黄汉升。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关兴、张苞同下。刘备下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "刘备→黄忠",
          "turns": 2
