    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "张嶷",
        "报子",
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四大铠、张嶷同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张嶷",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三国相争斗，将士用机谋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄老将军到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张嶷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下，黄忠上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张嶷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，老将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张嶷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将军到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军有所不知：只因关兴、张苞，在阵前擒得谭雄，无非是些小的功劳；我主"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "隆恩，在酒席宴前，夸了又夸，奖了又奖，分明是笑我老将无用。是我忿气出"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "营，要匹马单刀，去到阵前，活捉潘璋，生擒吴侯。那时方显我黄忠不老！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张嶷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你本来的老了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将军说话言蹊跷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由黄忠怒心梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你看我八十二岁老黄忠，哪些儿显老？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张嶷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你实实的老了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一言气坏将英豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "两军阵前立功劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
