    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "潘璋"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、潘璋同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘璋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾，东吴大将潘璋。自从关公被害，吴侯将他的刀马赐与某家。那赤兔马，不"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘璋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃草料而亡；这刀，到我手中，并未斩过上将。闻听黄忠，前来讨战，待我前"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘璋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去会他一会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘璋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，起兵前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
