    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "催马提刀把仗打",
        "崔玉",
        "潘璋",
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄忠上，崔玉、史纪同上，黄忠下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看黄忠，虽然败阵，他马蹄不乱。待我赶上，定要死在他手。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（崔玉、史纪同下。黄忠上，崔玉、史纪同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，你与我压住阵脚，待我摘这个老倭瓜！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄忠杀崔玉、史纪。崔玉、史纪同下。潘璋上，对阵。）"
